dct_title_s: Афины и Пирей (J-34-72,84) : Греция, номы Аттика, Пирей (J-34-72,84)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by 10 meter contour intervals and spot heights. Depth shown by 10 meter isolines and soundings. Sistema koordinat 1942 g. Military topographic map showing numbered government, military, transportation, and industrial facilities. Ancillary map: skhema linii metropolitena [map of the subway lines]. Includes text, indexes, and sheet-assembly diagrams. "Sostavleno v 1973g. Ispravleno po materialam na 1979,1981gg." "Составлено в 1973г. Исправлено по материалам на 1979,1981гг." "Sistema koordinat 1942 g." "Система координат 1942 г." Sheets numbered: List 1 [northern] -- List 2 [southern]. Sheets numbered: Лист 1 [northern] -- Лист 2 [southern]. Former security classification in margins: Sekretno. Former security classification in margins: Секретно. "I-18/1 XI-84-K. I-18/2 XI-84-K." "И-18/1 XI-84-К. И-18/2 XI-84-К." East Decimal Degree 23.850000. West Decimal Degree 23.583333. Former Soviet Union. Sovetskaiia Armiia Generl'nyi shtab. One map in two sheets. Relief shown by 10 m. contour interval and spot heights. Depths shown by 10 m.contour interval and soundings. Sistema koordinat 1942 g. Ancilary map: skhema linii metropolitena [subway line]. Map shows numbered government, military, transportation, and industrial facilities. "Sostavleno v 1973g. Ispravleno po materialam na 1979,1981gg."Sheets numbered: List 1 [northern]; List 2 [southern]. Former security classification in right margin: Sekretno."I-18/1 XI-84-K. I-18/2 XI-84-K.". North Decimal Degree 38.133333. South Decimal Degree 37.783333.
